title: Hour 3 - Frank Isola, Marcellus Wiley
itunes:title: Hour 3 - Frank Isola, Marcellus Wiley
description:
Dan speaks with NBA insider Frank Isola about the parting of ways between Steve Nash and the Brooklyn Nets. Plus he chats with NFL insider Marcellus Wiley about all the action during yesterday's NFL trade deadline.
